## Requirements

Administrators shall be able to:

- Create users
- Update users
- Deactivate users
- Reactivate users
- Assign roles
- Assign teams
- Reset passwords

## User Information

The platform shall maintain:

- Name
- Email
- Phone number
- Job title
- Team assignment
- Role assignment
- Status

