# Activity and Interaction Tracking

## Requirements

The platform shall allow users to record customer interactions.

Supported activity types include:

- Phone calls
- Meetings
- Emails
- Notes
- Follow-ups

Users shall be able to:

- Create activities
- Edit activities
- View activity history
- View customer timelines

All activities shall be associated with customers and optionally contacts.

---

# Sales Opportunity Management

## Requirements

Users shall be able to:

- Create opportunities
- Assign opportunities
- Update opportunities
- Move opportunities through pipeline stages
- Close opportunities as won or lost

## Opportunity Information

The platform shall support:

- Opportunity name
- Customer association
- Contact association
- Opportunity owner
- Expected revenue
- Probability
- Expected close date
- Opportunity stage

---

# Pipeline Management

## Requirements

The platform shall support visual pipeline management.

Users shall be able to:

- View opportunities by stage
- Move opportunities between stages
- Filter opportunities
- Search opportunities

Default stages include:

- Lead
- Qualified
- Proposal
- Negotiation
- Won
- Lost

Pipeline stages shall be configurable.

