# Non-Functional Requirements

## Performance

- Pages should load quickly under normal operating conditions.
- Search operations should return results efficiently.
- Dashboard metrics should remain responsive.

## Scalability

- The system must support growth in users, customers, contacts, and opportunities without significant degradation.

## Reliability

- The platform should provide high availability and fault tolerance.

## Security

- Sensitive information must be protected.
- All user actions must be authorized.
- Data access must respect role permissions.

## Usability

- The application must provide an intuitive user experience.
- The interface must be responsive across desktop and tablet devices.

## Maintainability

- The platform must support future enhancements and integrations.

---

